    "fix4_spectral": "v1 used FFT(u_pred) \u2014 correct near-shock predictions have high-freq content and were misclassified as spectral_bias. v2 uses FFT(u_pred - u_exact)/||u_exact||\u2082 \u2014 measures error frequency content, not prediction frequency content.",
